<div class="panel panel-primary" style="background-color:#FAFAFA">
<div class="panel-heading" style="font-size:18px"><strong>Cadastrar Subrede (dhcp.conf)</strong>
</div>
 <div class="panel-body">
    <div class="alert alert-info"> <p style="text-align:center; font-size:16px;"><strong> Obs: Todos os campos com asterisco são de preenchimento obrigatorio.<br>Ex: subnet 200.239.152.0 netmask 255.255.252.0 { option routers 200.239.152.2; }</strong> </p>
